u0107 wi\u0119cej klient\u00f3w.<\/li>\n<li><b>Zmieniaj kategorie, je\u015bli to konieczne<\/b>: Je\u015bli Tw\u00f3j produkt nie sprzedaje si\u0119 tak, jakby\u015b chcia\u0142, rozwa\u017c zmian\u0119 jego kategorii, aby poprawi\u0107 widoczno\u015b\u0107 i zwi\u0119kszy\u0107 sprzeda\u017c.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Podsumowuj\u0105c, BSR to istotny wska\u017anik, kt\u00f3ry odzwierciedla pr\u0119dko\u015b\u0107 sprzeda\u017cy, wska\u017aniki konwersji oraz mar\u017ce zysku. Regularnie monitoruj sw\u00f3j BSR i podejmuj dzia\u0142ania, aby optymalizowa\u0107 wyniki sprzeda\u017cy na Amazonie. Je\u015bli chcesz dowiedzie\u0107 si\u0119 wi\u0119cej o strategiach sprzeda\u017cy na Amazonie, \u015bled\u017a tre\u015bci Stephena Pope&#8217;a.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak wykorzysta\u0107 Best Seller Rank (BSR) w sprzeda\u017cy na Amazonie?<\/h1>\n<p>Czy wiesz, jak wa\u017cny jest <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":5114,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[2],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-5113","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-kontent"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5113"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5113"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5113\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/5114"}],"wp:attachment":[{"